metadata.title: AquaticHI 4 Pack Felt Filter Socks, 200 Micron, 4 Inch Ring by 8 Inch Long, for Freshwater/Saltwater Aquariums, Ponds, Use in Sumps/Overflows
features: ⭐️EXCELLENT MECHANICAL FILTRATION: The use of filters socks IMPROVES WATER QUALITY by trapping debris, detritus, excess food, sand, coral and more
⭐️HIGH QUALITY PROFESSIONAL GRADE: These filter socks are designed to be sturdy, strong, and heavy duty to be RE-USABLE and cleaned
⭐️CRYSTAL CLEAR WATER: These 200 micron felt filter socks trap smaller organic matter and debris that larger or mesh filter socks do not catch to provide crystal clear water
⭐️REDUCES NOISE AND SPLASH in your aquarium/pond overflow sump system
⭐️WHATS INCLUDED: 4x 4 inch ring by 8 inch long 200 micron felt filter sock
description: Improve your aquariums water quality and have crystal clear water in your display tank by using AquaticHI’s felt filter socks!

The AquaticHI felt filter sock was designed with an aquarium hobbyist in mind. The 200 micron catches and traps waste such as uneaten food, decaying plants, livestock, and organic matter that breaks down and produces unwanted ammonia in the tank. Smaller micron filters will also provide the same benefits but will clog and require cleaning/replacing more often.
- Improves water quality - Produces crystal clear water - Reduces noise and splash in sump
-4x 4 inch ring by 8 inch long 200 micron felt filter sock
